tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE NonprofitImpactData (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    program_id UUID,
    impact_type TEXT,
    impact_description TEXT,
    impact_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE impact_data (
	id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	initiative_id INT,
	impact_description TEXT,
	impact_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE outcomes (
	id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	initiative_id INT,
	outcome_description TEXT,
	outcome_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE initiatives (
	id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	initiative_name TEXT,
	start_date DATE,
	end_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE programs (
	id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	program_name TEXT,
	program_type TEXT,
	program_manager TEXT
)
